Trick: "Parallel but Not Coincident" - For no solution, $ rac{a_1}{a_2} =  rac{b_1}{b_2} 
e  rac{c_1}{c_2}$. Here, $ rac{3}{6} =  rac{-1}{-2} 
e  rac{5}{m}$. This simplifies to $ rac{1}{2} =  rac{1}{2} 
e  rac{5}{m}$. So, $ rac{1}{2} 
e  rac{5}{m} \Rightarrow m 
e 10$.

